import './index.css'; const About = () => (

About Us

Umuhinzi platform empowers farmers by making them informed thus able to make better decisions. When purchasing farm inputs through this platform, you will access the latest prices for input products. You will also get news on what is happening in the tea sector. If you do not have a smartphone, no worries. We have USSD services for you where you will get the same features. By dialing the provided code on your phone, you will access the services we have on the web app.

); export default About;
